import { Box, Button, Dialog,TextField, Typography , styled} from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Component = styled(Box)`

`

const LoginDialog = (props) => {
  const handleClose =() =>{
    props.setOpen(false)
  }
  return (
   <>
    <Dialog open={props.openDialog} onClose={handleClose}>
      <Box>
        <Box></Box>
        <Box>
        <TextField variant='standard' label="Enter Email/Number"/>
        <TextField variant='standard' label="Enter Password"/>
        <TextField>By continuing, you agree to Flipkart's Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.</TextField>
        <Button>Login</Button>
        <Typography>OR</Typography>
        <Button>Request OTP</Button>
        <Typography>New to Flipkart? Create an account</Typography>
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </Dialog>
   </>
  )
}

export default LoginDialog
